Devoted Spirit (Strike)
Level: Crusader 1, Saint 1
Initiation Action: 1 standard action
Range: Melee attack
Target: One creature

As part of initiating this strike, you must make a successful attack against an enemy whose alignment has at least one component different from yours. This foe must pose a threat to you or your allies in some direct, immediate way. If your attack hits, you or an ally within 10 feet of you heals 1d6 points of damage + 1 point per initiator level (maximum +5).
